      "instruction": "<p>Crush your <strong>garlic </strong>open by squashing with the side of a knife and discard the skin</p><p>Add your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> to the dish with your <strong>balsamic sundried tomato paste</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>dried basil</strong>, <strong>crushed</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Stir it all together and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
