    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your<strong> farfalle </strong>to the pot with your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and 500ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [650ml]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[850ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Tip: Nestle the farfalle into the stock as much as you can for even cooking!</p>",
